message.raw: Switched runtime dependency from libprotobuf7 to libprotobuf-dev because we need the protobuf headers in google/protobuf/stubs.  Our gazebo package is effectively a gazebo-dev package, so it's not surprising that we should depend on some underlying -dev packages.  Eventually we'll split up gazebo into gazebo gazebo-dev and gazebo-dbg.
